Overview

TrustBridge is a SaaS-grade backend platform for managing trust between customers, vendors, and platform admins.

It supports:

Customer accounts
Vendor business profiles
Admin moderation
Vendor discovery
Vendor trust scoring
Reviews and ratings
Scam/fraud reports
Disputes
Support/customer-care tickets
Real-time notifications
Webhooks
API keys
Billing/subscriptions
Audit logs
Redis caching
BullMQ background jobs
CI/CD testing
Roles
CUSTOMER

Customers can:

Search vendors
View top-rated vendors
Review vendors
Report vendors
Raise disputes
Contact support/customer care
VENDOR

Vendors can:

Register business profile
Add business details
Add CAC/NIN/category/description
View customer reviews
View reports/disputes
View trust score
Upload documents
Contact support
ADMIN

Admins can:

Verify vendors/documents
Manage reports
Manage disputes
Manage users/vendors
Handle support tickets
View audit logs
